    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Doctor. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.3ZerjLH8ls3JT6cD]{Robust Recovery}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Medicine checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1kGNdIIhuglAjIp9]{Treat Wounds}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.TC7OcDa7JlWbqMaN]{Treat Disease}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.KjoCEEmPGTeFE4hh]{Treat Poison}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Kk4AMZtpQnLEgN0b]{Legendary Medic}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
